text: Polyana () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Tryokhprotoksky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km WSW from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Polyana, Astrakhan Oblast
